# 📊 Smart Research Statistics Assistant (SRSA)

SRSA is an AI-powered app that helps researchers analyze data, run statistical tests, visualize surveys, and generate publication-ready outputs in APA format — with plain-English explanations.

## ✨ Features
- Upload SPSS, Excel, R, or CSV files
- Auto-clean & check statistical assumptions
- Run t-tests, ANOVA, Chi-square, regression
- Auto-generate APA-style outputs
- Visualize survey data (Likert, bar, pie)
- AI-generated interpretations using OpenAI

## 🚀 Run the App
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
